- do not claim fixes are shipped unless explicitly stated
- keep the tone human and concise
- if the issue is Trade Republic sync reliability, state that it is treated as a top-priority reliability topic

Context:
ticket_id: ${j.ticket_id}
customer_email: ${j.customer_email}
subscription_tier: ${j.subscription_tier}
category: ${j.category}
